    {
      "id": 37796,
      "name": "Section Info",
      "hint": "Some info below",
      "color": { "rank": 1, "color": "#75E45B", "id": 1847, "name": "Green" },
      "colorCode": "Green",
      "type": "Information",
      "text": "<p>This is my info I wanted to show...</p>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 30px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 36px; color: rgb(35, 32, 25); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Coegit sorbentur coeperunt tum derecti</h1>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 9px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(35, 32, 25); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Tuti aliis mutastis locum tepescunt evolvit silvas ita. Onus nisi mundi terrae. Deducite diversa cuncta. Formaeque mixtam. Alta fulgura ad traxit quem discordia diverso hanc. Utramque discordia recepta! Pugnabant tumescere aurea altae deerat fert egens his passim. Caeli silvas sua silvas quanto matutinis sinistra.</p>\n<h2 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 24px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 36px; color: rgb(35, 32, 25); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><em>Illic</em> <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">meis</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(241, 196, 15);\">proximus</span> <span style=\"background-color: rgb(185, 106, 217);\">et</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(224, 62, 45);\">caelum</span></h2>\n<h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 18px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(35, 32, 25); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Ipsa glomeravit praeter convexi usu</h3>\n<h4 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(35, 32, 25); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Derecti obstabatque pace nebulas traxit</h4>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 9px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(35, 32, 25); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Madescit flamina adsiduis caelum lege. Terrae nisi undis formaeque recens totidemque. Fabricator mundi rerum sine. Descenderat semina spectent crescendo addidit peregrinum dispositam quicquam? Ne discordia finxit nabataeaque. Quicquam radiis aera iapeto subsidere ulla omnia ripis obliquis.</p>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px 0px 9px 25px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; color: rgb(35, 32, 25); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 12px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: disc; line-height: 18px;\">Quisque tellure galeae mundum locis pace proxima rectumque pro verba instabilis</li>\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 12px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: disc; line-height: 18px;\">Aequalis ita rudis obliquis aquae fidem erant montibus sui tumescere sic facientes partim madescit exemit fossae omnia pressa tenent moles ardentior</li>\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 12px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: disc; line-height: 18px;\">Ventis liberioris ita usu nitidis dicere solidumque totidemque origine regat emicuit aquae oppida pronaque diu locis abscidit spectent cura longo</li>\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 12px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: disc; line-height: 18px;\">Finxit subdita onerosior haec nisi iapeto tepescunt amphitrite fronde homo liquidas aestu pronaque cognati tumescere vis finxit ardentior flamma ultima distinxit</li>\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 12px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: disc; line-height: 18px;\">Lacusque duae eodem cepit omni certis cura timebat vindice diversa iapeto lanient animal fabricator flamma nullaque astra inminet</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 9px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(35, 32, 25); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Derecti dissaepserat? Toto calidis extendi. Ultima habitabilis prima septemque pinus tenent. Tellure pulsant tumescere. Quinta videre fuit carmen feras metusque quicquam sinistra. Circumfuso congestaque diverso nisi terrenae galeae undis nebulas? Triones chaos: caeca fossae iuga?</p>\n<ol style=\"margin: 0px 0px 9px 25px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; color: rgb(35, 32, 25); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 12px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: decimal; line-height: 18px;\">Omni aequalis duas ripis terras peregrinum foret quanto montes securae gravitate origo mutastis humanas tollere corpore quanto</li>\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 12px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: decimal; line-height: 18px;\">Fabricator mundum pro surgere seductaque lucis pontus natura utramque natus sole viseret perveniunt principio iners terram aliis liberioris tollere moderantum fratrum fulgura addidit</li>\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 12px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: decimal; line-height: 18px;\">Viseret aethere auroram liquidas vis pondere iuga zephyro spectent securae crescendo fixo rapidisque semina galeae mundum ut alta vix corpore subdita dominari quae</li>\n</ol>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 9px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(35, 32, 25); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Quae speciem mundo undis. Est semine sua discordia porrexerat. Corpora inclusum est figuras aurea erat non nitidis. Silvas locis indigestaque fabricator inmensa nec. Amphitrite obliquis effervescere illic his! Forma habentem. Aequalis mundum tanta animalia mundi corpore norant non inclusum.</p>",
